   "source": [
    "# 🏗️ Heatmap Temporal — Inversión Pública en el Perú (2017–2026)\n",
    "\n",
    "Visualización geoespacial animada de los proyectos de inversión pública registrados año a año en el Perú.\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Nota metodológica:** Las coordenadas georreferenciadas están disponibles desde 2017. Los proyectos anteriores existen en el dataset pero sin ubicación precisa (el MEF inició la georreferenciación obligatoria en INVIERTE.PE ese año).\n",
    "\n",
    "**Fuente:** MEF – Banco de Inversiones / Plataforma Nacional de Datos Abiertos  \n",
    "**Variable temporal:** Año de registro del proyecto (`FECHA_REGISTRO`)  \n",
    "**Intensidad:** Monto viable (S/.)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Autor:** Leo Molina (@leydimolina20)\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "▶️ **Ejecuta las 3 celdas en orden.**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ── CELDA 1: Dependencias ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "!pip install folium --quiet"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ── CELDA 2: Carga y procesamiento ───────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "import requests, io, gzip, warnings\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n",
    "\n",
    "# ── Descargar dataset desde GitHub ───────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "print('⏳ Descargando dataset de inversiones...')\n",
    "BASE = 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leydimolina20/peru-investment-headmap/main/data'\n",
    "raw = requests.get(f'{BASE}/inversiones_historico.gz').content\n",
    "df = pd.read_csv(io.BytesIO(gzip.decompress(raw)), low_memory=False)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'✅ {len(df):,} proyectos georreferenciados')\n",
    "print(f'📅 Años disponibles: {int(df[\"ANIO\"].min())}–{int(df[\"ANIO\"].max())}')\n",
    "print(f'💰 Monto total viable: S/. {df[\"MONTO_VIABLE\"].sum()/1e9:.1f} mil millones')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Resumen por año\n",
    "resumen = df.groupby('ANIO').agg(\n",
    "    proyectos=('MONTO_VIABLE','count'),\n",
    "    monto_MM=('MONTO_VIABLE', lambda x: round(x.sum()/1e6, 1))\n",
    ").reset_index()\n",
    "print('\\nProyectos y monto por año:')\n",
    "print(resumen.to_string(index=False))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ── CELDA 3: Heatmap animado por año ─────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "import folium\n",
    "from folium.plugins import HeatMapWithTime, Fullscreen, MiniMap\n",
    "\n",
    "YEARS = sorted(df['ANIO'].dropna().unique().astype(int))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Preparar datos por año (peso normalizado por monto)\n",
    "heat_data = []\n",
    "for yr in YEARS:\n",
    "    sub = df[df['ANIO'] == yr].copy()\n",
    "    cap = sub['MONTO_VIABLE'].quantile(0.95)\n",
    "    sub['peso'] = (sub['MONTO_VIABLE'].clip(upper=cap) / cap).fillna(0.05)\n",
    "    heat_data.append(sub[['LATITUD','LONGITUD','peso']].values.tolist())\n",
    "\n",
    "# Mapa base\n",
    "m = folium.Map(\n",
    "    location=[-9.5, -74.5],\n",
    "    zoom_start=5,\n",
    "    tiles='CartoDB dark_matter'\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# HeatMap animado\n",
    "HeatMapWithTime(\n",
    "    data=heat_data,\n",
    "    index=[str(y) for y in YEARS],\n",
    "    radius=15,\n",
    "    blur=12,\n",
    "    max_opacity=0.85,\n",
    "    min_opacity=0.05,\n",
    "    gradient={0.2:'#1565C0', 0.4:'#26A69A', 0.6:'#FFC107', 0.8:'#FF5722', 1.0:'#B71C1C'},\n",
    "    auto_play=True,\n",
    "    display_index=True,\n",
    "    time_interval=900,\n",
    "    speed_step=0.1,\n",
    ").add_to(m)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Controles\n",
    "Fullscreen(position='topright', title='Pantalla completa',\n",
    "           title_cancel='Salir', force_separate_button=True).add_to(m)\n",
    "MiniMap(toggle_display=True, position='bottomleft').add_to(m)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Título\n",
    "m.get_root().html.add_child(folium.Element(\"\"\"\n",
    "<div style=\"position:fixed;top:10px;left:50px;z-index:9999;\n",
    "    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.80);padding:12px 18px;border-radius:8px;\n",
    "    color:white;font-family:Arial;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)\">\n",
    "  <h3 style=\"margin:0;font-size:17px\">🏗️ Expansión de la Inversión Pública en el Perú</h3>\n",
    "  <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#90CAF9\">\n",
    "    2017–2026 · 130,884 proyectos · Intensidad = Monto viable (S/.)\n",
    "  </p>\n",
    "</div>\"\"\"))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Fuente\n",
    "m.get_root().html.add_child(folium.Element(\"\"\"\n",
    "<div style=\"position:fixed;top:10px;right:50px;z-index:9999;\n",
    "    color:#ccc;font-family:Arial;font-size:11px;\n",
    "    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.55);padding:6px 10px;border-radius:5px\">\n",
    "  Fuente: MEF – Banco de Inversiones INVIERTE.PE | Elaborado por: Leo Molina\n",
    "</div>\"\"\"))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Leyenda\n",
    "m.get_root().html.add_child(folium.Element(\"\"\"\n",
    "<div style=\"position:fixed;bottom:60px;right:10px;z-index:9999;\n",
    "    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.75);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:7px;\n",
    "    color:white;font-family:Arial;font-size:11px\">\n",
    "  <b>Intensidad de inversión</b><br>\n",
    "  <span style='color:#B71C1C'>■</span> Muy alta<br>\n",
    "  <span style='color:#FF5722'>■</span> Alta<br>\n",
    "  <span style='color:#FFC107'>■</span> Media<br>\n",
    "  <span style='color:#26A69A'>■</span> Baja<br>\n",
    "  <span style='color:#1565C0'>■</span> Muy baja\n",
    "</div>\"\"\"))\n",
    "\n",
    "m.save('inversiones_heatmap_temporal.html')\n",
    "print('✅ Mapa guardado como: inversiones_heatmap_temporal.html')\n",
    "m"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ── CELDA 4 (opcional): Top sectores por monto ───────────────────────────────\n",
    "top_sectores = (\n",
    "    df.groupby('SECTOR')\n",
    "    .agg(proyectos=('MONTO_VIABLE','count'),\n",
    "         monto_MM=('MONTO_VIABLE', lambda x: round(x.sum()/1e6,1)))\n",
    "    .sort_values('monto_MM', ascending=False)\n",
    "    .head(15)\n",
    "    .reset_index()\n",
    ")\n",
    "print('Top 15 sectores por monto viable (millones S/.)')\n",
    "top_sectores"
   ]
  }
 ],
